      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crank to reach an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. The chassis maintains its composure through Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a carbon fiber roof that lowers the center of gravity. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the powertrain. Suspension bushings and subframe mounts remain firm, providing precise turn-in and predictable lateral dynamics. A mechanically sound, driver-focused machine for the serious enthusiast.",
